data.description: Nestled in the community of Live Oaks, This ideal location for everything Beaufort has to offer features a Beautiful kitchen with granite counter tops all appliances included with washer and dryer. Privacy fenced backyard for outdoor entertainment. Enjoy new flooring throughout main living areas. The open living concept allows for everyday living/entertaining made simple. Kitchen has plenty of counter/cabinet space, under cabinet lighting.
